            "title": "深股跌近2.5%  一周計A股報升滬股升逾1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股午後跌擴大，深股以全日低位收市，跌近2.5%，創板蹟.65%，一周計滬股升逾1%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/05/20250508_FI_source-ap_AShare-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/05/20250508_FI_source-ap_AShare-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬綜指全日收報3,814，跌62點或1.61%，早段見3,861，跌15點或0.38%，為全日高位，跌幅隨即擴大，午後跌幅擴大，尾段低見3,808，跌68點或1.75%，全日成交9,153.66億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深成指全日收報13,774點，跌348點或2.47%，以全日低位收市，早段見14,061，跌62點或0.43%，為全日高位，隨即反覆向下，全日成交10,157.74   億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300全日跌78點或1.67%，報4,649點 ; 創業板指數全日跌94點或2.65%，報3,480點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">一周累計滬綜指升50點或1.32% ; 深成指升68點或0.49%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/16428978-%e6%b7%b1%e8%82%a1%e8%b7%8c%e8%bf%912-5-%e4%b8%80%e5%91%a8%e8%a8%88a%e8%82%a1%e5%a0%b1%e5%8d%87%e6%bb%ac%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be1",
